==發行==
2015年11月，[[亞馬遜影業|亞馬遜影業]]收購了電影在美國的發行權<ref>{{cite news|last1=Evry|first1=Max|title=Amazon Acquires The Neon Demon, Plus New Elle Fanning Image|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/631161-amazon-acquires-the-neon-demon-plus-new-elle-fanning-image|accessdate=2015-11-10|work=comingsoon.net|date=2015-11-09|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115214111/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/631161-amazon-acquires-the-neon-demon-plus-new-elle-fanning-image|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本片於2016年5月的[[第69屆坎城影展|第69屆坎城影展]]上首映<ref name="IW"/><ref name="VarCannes"/>。在美國於2016年6月24日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/neon-demon-trailer-first-look-at-nicolas-winding-refns-horror-film-1201753752/|title=‘Neon Demon’ Trailer: First Look at Nicolas Winding Refn’s Horror Film|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Variety|last=Staff|date=2016-04-14|accessdate=2016-04-18|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117232043/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/neon-demon-trailer-first-look-at-nicolas-winding-refns-horror-film-1201753752/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ocregister.com/articles/young-714052-new-world.html|title=See all the 2016 summer movies|website=OcRegister.com|first=Rob|last=Lowman|date=2016-04-28|accessdate=2016-04-29|archive-date=2017-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110122719/http://www.ocregister.com/articles/young-714052-new-world.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而香港則於2017年5月5日直接推出DVD，並没有於電影院公映。

==反響==
